00:43:28.000 --> 00:43:29.660
And I think that's
an important thing,

00:43:29.660 --> 00:43:31.368
is when we write things
and convey things

00:43:31.368 --> 00:43:34.840
that we aspire with our head
and we pine with our hearts.

00:43:34.840 --> 00:43:37.500
We crave with our bodies, right,
