00:44:16.250 --> 00:44:17.715
how you [INAUDIBLE]?

00:44:17.715 --> 00:44:19.580
RAJIV SATYAL: I think
the ones that we

00:44:19.580 --> 00:44:21.890
wrote for-- so a friend
of mine and I in LA,

00:44:21.890 --> 00:44:24.630
we co-wrote a couple of
