00:50:47.100 --> 00:50:48.930
love the Alabama Crimson Tide.

00:50:48.930 --> 00:50:49.680
They went crazy.

00:50:49.680 --> 00:50:50.890
Oh my god, this guy knows.

00:50:50.890 --> 00:50:51.390
Right?

00:50:51.390 --> 00:50:56.350
So you need to say something
specific that will get people.

00:50:56.350 --> 00:51:00.550
I do a joke about how
I was trying to-- I

00:51:00.550 --> 00:51:02.600
