00:51:02.600 --> 00:51:06.130
It's not really shoddy,
it's shoddy-- S-H-O-D-D-Y--

00:51:06.130 --> 00:51:07.840
shoddy.com.

00:51:07.840 --> 00:51:09.270
Or shady.com, right?

00:51:09.270 --> 00:51:10.820
And so I was on that.

00:51:10.820 --> 00:51:14.015
And it asked all these questions
and it asked if I was a manglik

00:51:14.015 --> 00:51:16.080
And I didn't know what
a manglik was, you know?

00:51:16.080 --> 00:51:18.240
So I looked it up online.

00:51:18.240 --> 00:51:19.710
And I always did
a joke about how

00:51:19.710 --> 00:51:21.610
I felt bad looking
up my culture online.

00:51:21.610 --> 00:51:23.080
But so many Indians
